==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Inserted
<hw>In*sert"ed</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Situated upon,
attached to, or growing out of, some part; -- said especially of the
parts of the flower; <as>as, the calyx, corolla, and stamens of many
flowers are <ex>inserted</ex> upon the receptacle</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Gray.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Inserting</ent>⟦br⟧
